  m_text: "HAND TRACKING \r\r\n\r\nThe app will continuously track your left or right
    hand position. This is represented as red lines overlapped onto your real hand.
    White balls represent the location of each joint. Look at your right hand now
    to see this representation. Move your right hand and fingers around to see how
    the tracking works. It should look like the image on the right. Please say \"calibrate\"
    to calibrate the system to your hand. You will see \"Calibration Complete\" when
    this is finished.\n\nTo proceed to the next set of instructions, say \"Instructions
    Part 2\""
