      value: "GOAL \r\n\n   \rThe goal is to provide hand function feedback when
        grasping different objects \r\n\r\nNAVIGATE APP WITH YOUR VOICE \r\n\r\r\nThe
        app recognizes a specific set of words. For example, say \"dictionary on\"
        to see all the available words that can be used to navigate through the app.
