      propertyPath: m_text
      value: " \r\n\n   \rThe goal is to provide hand function feedback when grasping
        different objects \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\r\nThe app recognizes a specific set of
        words. You will see prompts as you use the app to make it easier to navigate.
        \n\nIf you need to see all of the words that the app will recognize, say
        \"dictionary on\". Then say \"dictionary off\" to remove the dictionary from
        the screen."
