      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The purpose of the feedback is to show you the comparison between your
    grasping posture and the target grasping posture. The second way you will get
    feedback is by overlapping your posture (blue lines) onto the target posture
    (yellow lines). This feedback will be in the top left corner of the screen. This
    feedback will help you see the difference in the posture of each of your fingers.
    This feedback and the quantitative feedback will both appear at the same time.
    Note that when you say \u201Cperformance\u201D or \u201Cscore\u201D it is important
    to try and keep your head still until all the feedback appears. See below for
    an example. "
